      <title>乌拉圭的奥尔西赢得广泛阵线初选，任命科斯为副总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/uruguay-s-orsi-leads-left-wing-opposition-presidential-primary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前州长亚曼杜·奥尔西 (Yamandu Orsi) 周日晚间赢得左翼政党广泛阵线 (Broad Front) 的总统初选后，选定政治对手卡罗莱纳·科斯 (Carolina Cosse) 为其竞选搭档。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/uruguay-s-orsi-leads-left-wing-opposition-presidential-primary</guid>
